@dev Provides a read-through expiring cache in front of the Vault's role based governance
 - A cached role expires when an access finds an expired TTL, this results in an external get/set
 - This technique saves gas in a tight loop such as with `safeTransferFrom`
 @param account Address of the caller
 @return role The role for `account`

